 👋 Hi, I'm Jayati Verma

### 🌿 Wellness-Focused Mobile App Developer | React Native & Flutter | Firebase Champion

I'm a cross-platform app developer with **4.8 years** of experience crafting delightful, scalable mobile experiences across **fitness**, **health-tech**, and **automotive** domains.

- 💪 Currently building [**FitNest**](https://github.com/jayativerma/fitnest-rn-app) — a bougie, animated workout tracker with Firebase, Lottie, and streak logic
- 🚗 Previously contributed to **Jaguar Land Rover** and **Philips Healthcare** apps via TCS
- ✨ Obsessed with UI animations, glassmorphism, LottieFX, and beautiful UX journeys
- 📲 Skilled in React Native, Flutter, Firebase, GraphQL, Expo, Redux, Provider

